#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:3 2f1b0b2ec716415e9b35d39612795279
msgid "ComfyUI-VoxCPM"
msgstr "ComfyUI-VoxCPM"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:5 c9ad7c14e20d47d9ac98f0f55b2e79aa
msgid ""
"ComfyUI-VoxCPM is a full-featured ComfyUI custom node for VoxCPM, with TTS, "
"voice cloning, and **in-node LoRA training** support."
msgstr "ComfyUI-VoxCPM 是面向 VoxCPM 的全功能 ComfyUI 自定义节点，支持 TTS、声音克隆以及 **节点内 LoRA 训练**。"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:7 0047bc9da632491486c2648dafae9904
msgid ""
"Repo: `wildminder/ComfyUI-VoxCPM <https://github.com/wildminder/ComfyUI-"
"VoxCPM>`_"
msgstr ""
"仓库：`wildminder/ComfyUI-VoxCPM <https://github.com/wildminder/ComfyUI-"
"VoxCPM>`_"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:9 e097d7d152124c1ca91df27454d323a4
msgid ""
"It wraps VoxCPM into ComfyUI's visual node-based workflow, allowing users to"
" integrate speech synthesis into their generation pipelines."
msgstr "它将 VoxCPM 接入 ComfyUI 的可视化节点工作流，便于在生成管线中集成语音合成。"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:12 94a0558cdd1d455d81265cc6c057f6cb
msgid ""
"For a lighter alternative with auto-transcription, see "
":doc:`comfyui_voxcpmtts`."
msgstr "若需要更轻量且带自动转写的方案，请参阅 :doc:`comfyui_voxcpmtts`。"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:14 2edec3520b1643a79eb767f669f92e46
msgid "Supported VoxCPM Versions"
msgstr "支持的 VoxCPM 版本"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:18 f7e405d6f47744af8de0c2ac43710a83
msgid "VoxCPM 1.0 (0.5B)"
msgstr "VoxCPM 1.0 (0.5B)"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:19 2763521cce7a44b8a73256fabcc17673
msgid "✅ Supported (``openbmb/VoxCPM-0.5B``, 16 kHz)"
msgstr "✅ 支持（``openbmb/VoxCPM-0.5B``，16 kHz）"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:20 b4e74b8e42514dcab97e61affc73e179
msgid "VoxCPM 1.5"
msgstr "VoxCPM 1.5"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:21 9e82728b3b804b89b0ab81f56238760d
msgid "✅ Supported (``openbmb/VoxCPM1.5``, 44.1 kHz)"
msgstr "✅ 支持（``openbmb/VoxCPM1.5``，44.1 kHz）"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:22 12d2cb0c90c849ceaa5f8611e4c9c452
msgid "VoxCPM 2"
msgstr "VoxCPM 2"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:23 07dd1304f4c74f95875086ca319006c9
msgid "❌ Not supported"
msgstr "❌ 不支持"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:26 204a7b6c52184adc9f5b1b7baa4b1d6d
msgid "Features"
msgstr "主要特性"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:28 cf31fab0d42446f98e965cff3243ccbe
msgid ""
"Supports both **VoxCPM 1.5** (44.1 kHz, ~800M params) and **VoxCPM-0.5B** "
"(16 kHz, ~640M params)"
msgstr "同时支持 VoxCPM 1.5（44.1 kHz，约 8 亿参数）与 VoxCPM-0.5B（16 kHz，约 6.4 亿参数）"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:29 f9cc3493efa54e3489f3d19a324c3e2c
msgid "Auto-download models to ``ComfyUI/models/tts/VoxCPM/``"
msgstr "自动下载模型到 ``ComfyUI/models/tts/VoxCPM/``"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:30 65822c4bb58848b3b140e951a6100884
msgid "**LoRA inference and training** directly in ComfyUI:"
msgstr "在 ComfyUI 内直接进行 **LoRA 推理与训练**："

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:32 09143b7b7bd544138481980b5f75ae39
msgid "``VoxCPM Train Config`` — configure training hyperparameters"
msgstr "``VoxCPM Train Config`` — 配置训练超参数"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:33 c46a72e11ece401495d20ea266fc92a8
msgid "``VoxCPM Dataset Maker`` — prepare fine-tuning data"
msgstr "``VoxCPM Dataset Maker`` — 准备微调数据"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:34 d52064aa4d5b4d08afb0d9955f78ab5c
msgid "``VoxCPM LoRA Trainer`` — run LoRA fine-tuning within ComfyUI"
msgstr "``VoxCPM LoRA Trainer`` — 在 ComfyUI 内运行 LoRA 微调"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:36 372fa0b9f0444dc6915b4daaed242782
msgid "All generation parameters exposed as node inputs"
msgstr "生成相关参数均作为节点输入暴露"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:37 ef27925c27e54594b7218c73d381edae
msgid ""
"Built-in denoiser (ZipEnhancer) disabled by default to keep dependencies "
"light"
msgstr "内置降噪（ZipEnhancer）默认关闭，以减轻依赖"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:38 c1f40741dcec48ce93a421892775136c
msgid ""
"Multi-device support: **CUDA**, **CPU**, **MPS** (Apple Silicon), "
"**DirectML**, **HIP** (AMD ROCm, if available)"
msgstr ""
"多设备： **CUDA**、**CPU**、**MPS** （Apple Silicon）、**DirectML**、**HIP** （AMD "
"ROCm，若可用）"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:41 225b0b549dc04c1389fa63b5447c6a81
msgid "Prerequisites"
msgstr "准备工作"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:43 3bb26a07a99140f38ce37ec7c33f3b5e
msgid "`ComfyUI <https://github.com/comfyanonymous/ComfyUI>`_ installed and running"
msgstr "已安装并运行 `ComfyUI <https://github.com/comfyanonymous/ComfyUI>`_"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:44 6be6e187e4ec49b8a6e51c421e332976
msgid "PyTorch with appropriate backend (CUDA, MPS, etc.)"
msgstr "已安装匹配后端的 PyTorch（CUDA、MPS 等）"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:45 ca00368d61b04cab8bc08cf14b8645dd
msgid ""
"Model weights: `openbmb/VoxCPM1.5 "
"<https://huggingface.co/openbmb/VoxCPM1.5>`_ or `openbmb/VoxCPM-0.5B "
"<https://huggingface.co/openbmb/VoxCPM-0.5B>`_ (auto-downloaded)"
msgstr ""
"模型权重：`openbmb/VoxCPM1.5 <https://huggingface.co/openbmb/VoxCPM1.5>`_ 或 "
"`openbmb/VoxCPM-0.5B <https://huggingface.co/openbmb/VoxCPM-0.5B>`_ （自动下载）"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:48 2f4a43e4d4dc407881f20ab9455adc14
msgid "Installation"
msgstr "安装"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:50 f58357f7f68146da934fbfed50adc2c8
msgid "Via ComfyUI Manager: search for ``ComfyUI-VoxCPM`` and install."
msgstr "通过 ComfyUI Manager：搜索 ``ComfyUI-VoxCPM`` 并安装。"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:52 0413d1de64e84dda874849743e130df3
msgid "Manual installation:"
msgstr "手动安装："

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:61 7b94e7b24d644c6b9e90e986d000d805
msgid "Models are auto-downloaded on first use."
msgstr "首次使用时会自动下载模型。"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:64 712406acb2044562b13dd8a36504dadf
msgid "Basic usage"
msgstr "基本用法"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:67 f562f61766e7423dba817b4ceb27f9b4
msgid "Text-to-Speech"
msgstr "文本转语音"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:69 02e02ccca251478c80d7a78c92c99688
msgid "Add a **VoxCPM TTS** node from the ``audio/tts`` category"
msgstr "从 ``audio/tts`` 分类添加 **VoxCPM TTS** 节点"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:70 193e051bd595406aa79bfcab6deada8f
msgid "Connect ``text`` input with the target text to synthesize"
msgstr "将 ``text`` 输入连接到待合成文本"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:71 43ca05dda8c4420b880cb42b8c5ebb71
msgid "Adjust ``cfg_value``, ``inference_timesteps``, and ``device`` as needed"
msgstr "按需调节 ``cfg_value``、``inference_timesteps`` 与 ``device``"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:72 952cecebbf6746008176a3fc7b5e03d3
msgid "Connect output to a ``Save Audio`` or ``Preview Audio`` node"
msgstr "将输出接到 ``Save Audio`` 或 ``Preview Audio`` 节点"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:75 73af069cd75945989c14792da7fa1e2f
msgid "Voice cloning"
msgstr "声音克隆"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:77 c848cbc7a0ee4968a7ec577a9614eea8
msgid "Add a **Load Audio** node and load your reference audio"
msgstr "添加 **Load Audio** 节点并载入参考音频"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:78 524f79decbd24a258fbb4edf54e28393
msgid "Connect it to the ``prompt_audio`` input of the VoxCPM TTS node"
msgstr "将其接到 VoxCPM TTS 节点的 ``prompt_audio`` 输入"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:79 eb53fa256bcf40e98829e6ed68b08e23
msgid ""
"Provide the **verbatim transcript** in ``prompt_text`` (not a description — "
"must match the reference audio exactly)"
msgstr "在 ``prompt_text`` 中提供 **逐字转写** （不是描述，须与参考音频完全一致）"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:80 311b8947c7754a208d8187cd25f30bb0
msgid "Enter the target text to synthesize in ``text``"
msgstr "在 ``text`` 中输入要合成的目标文本"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:83 64b5602feac64192ab41ed25f6cad8af
msgid ""
"For high-quality voice clones, use clear reference audio (5–15 seconds) and "
"ensure ``prompt_text`` is an accurate transcript."
msgstr "要获得高质量克隆，请使用清晰参考音频（5–15 秒），并保证 ``prompt_text`` 转写准确。"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:86 ef6bd7419c7242708492ba51fbba951e
msgid "LoRA fine-tuning"
msgstr "LoRA 微调"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:88 712fdd6d525c4745ab04301890f8f5de
msgid ""
"Add ``VoxCPM Train Config`` → ``VoxCPM Dataset Maker`` → ``VoxCPM LoRA "
"Trainer`` nodes"
msgstr ""
"依次添加 ``VoxCPM Train Config`` → ``VoxCPM Dataset Maker`` → ``VoxCPM LoRA "
"Trainer`` 节点"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:89 32c97d1c93df4e4da4c0b4fd3bc7b307
msgid "Configure your training data and hyperparameters"
msgstr "配置训练数据与超参数"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:90 dd6d717a7c7c4a3fbb2d9704f3143883
msgid "Run the workflow to train a LoRA adapter"
msgstr "运行工作流以训练 LoRA 适配器"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:91 086d4838e522475b898de3605b86d9a3
msgid ""
"Load the trained LoRA from ``models/loras`` (use the refresh button and "
"``lora_name`` dropdown)"
msgstr "从 ``models/loras`` 加载训练好的 LoRA（使用刷新按钮与 ``lora_name`` 下拉框）"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:93 2b7dd578092e4efeae7021b6bd3c4a1e
msgid ""
"See ``readme-lora-training.md`` in the repository for detailed training "
"instructions."
msgstr "详细训练说明见仓库中的 ``readme-lora-training.md``。"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:96 813510e2e2d4459cabf81b312df32592
msgid "Parameters"
msgstr "参数说明"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:102 20622a4b74c743c09be32a6033540033
msgid "Parameter"
msgstr "参数"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:103 94f82db79da24d8e8b01acef260f515c
msgid "Description"
msgstr "说明"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:104 d9327315f2644db0b34551cb5a8ba22c
msgid "``model_name``"
msgstr "``model_name``"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:105 c9c3e188c6464a02852b5e8b579a6d45
msgid "Select VoxCPM 1.5 or 0.5B"
msgstr "选择 VoxCPM 1.5 或 0.5B"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:106 67978af451314c1d8812a37e6acfc1b8
msgid "``cfg_value``"
msgstr "``cfg_value``"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:107 d735261a6aa342bcbab8f0637fc9676b
msgid ""
"Classifier-free guidance scale (default: 2.0; higher = closer to prompt, may"
" reduce quality)"
msgstr "Classifier-free guidance 强度（默认 2.0；越大越贴近提示，可能损害音质）"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:108 ff716c7e077b4617ad6dd889662bb90c
msgid "``inference_timesteps``"
msgstr "``inference_timesteps``"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:109 c83c043c2c23483f83ebd60fd1b63e03
msgid "LocDiT diffusion steps (default: 10; higher = better quality, slower)"
msgstr "LocDiT 扩散步数（默认 10；越大质量通常越好、越慢）"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpm.rst:110 db04902da8db44d1a37d4d7b47409e8e
